    "title": "Dineout Capital India is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Lead)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Dineout Capital India! We are hiring a Guest Relations Manager for our Vadodara team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Dineout Capital India:\nDineout Capital India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dineout Capital India!",
